'''佳能EOS 1000D'''是一款1,010万[[像素|像素]]的数码单镜反光相机，由日本[[佳能公司|佳能公司]]制造。于2008年8月上市。它在日本被称作'''EOS Kiss F'''，在美国和加拿大也被称作'''EOS Rebel XS'''。EOS 1000D是一款入门级别的数位单反，被描述成“比[[佳能EOS_450D|佳能EOS 450D]]略差”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dpreview.com/reviews/canoneos1000d|title=Canon EOS 1000D（Rebel XS / Kiss F）Review|last=Butler|first=Richard|date=July 2008|publisher=dpreview.com|accessdate=November 20, 2009|archive-date=2019-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024042350/http://www.dpreview.com/reviews/canoneos1000d/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。相机与EOS 450D有一些共同的特点<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.canon-europe.com/For_Home/Product_Finder/Cameras/Digital_SLR/EOS_1000D/index.asp?specs=1|title=EOS 1000D   Product Specification|publisher=Canon Europe|accessdate=20 November 2009|archive-date=2009-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090728040127/http://www.canon-europe.com/For_Home/Product_Finder/Cameras/Digital_SLR/EOS_1000D/index.asp?specs=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite press release | title = CANON'S NEW EOS REBEL XS CAMERA LOOKS TO INSPIRE A NEW GENERATION OF DIGITAL SLR PHOTOGRAPHERS | publisher = Canon USA | date = July 8, 2008 | url = http://www.usa.canon.com/templatedata/pressrelease/20080708_rebel_xs.html | accessdate = November 20, 2009 | archive-date = 2021-11-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211122130030/https://www.usa.canon.com/templatedata/pressrelease/20080708_rebel_xs.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。它提供了[[实时取景|实时取景]]（即可以在液晶螢幕上取景）。不过，这款相机只有7个自动对焦点，也不带有点测光。该款相机使用[[SD卡|SD卡]]，而不是[[CF卡|CF卡]]。

